  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK618">
<l>poṟiyiṉmai yārkkum paḻiyaṉ ṟaṟivaṟin </l>
<l>tāḷviṉai yiṉmai paḻi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Adverse fate is no disgrace to any one; to be without exertion and without knowing what should be known, is disgrace.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
